data.description: *****PRE-FORECLOSURE******* Whether you’re an entertainer or a homebody, don’t miss this opportunity to own a truly one-of-a-kind modern solar powered home. Built in 2019, no detail was spared in this stunning 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom Home. As soon as you step through the tall glass front door, you’ll be greeted with soaring 9-foot ceilings and an open floor plan that’s decorated to impress. The beautiful kitchen showcases quartz counter-tops and gleaming stainless steel appliances, while the entire property effortlessly blends luxury with comfort. Recharge your batteries with the complete, fully-paid solar system, and enjoy private time in the covered lanai in the backyard that is fully-fenced for added security and privacy. With a convenient location near Hwy 27 and Posner Park Mall and more stores under construction, living in this home couldn’t be easier. Even better, a comprehensive home warranty is included! Don't miss out on this remarkable chance to own a truly unique modern home that can’t be replicated.
